29
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:14,250
Xue Ranran.

30
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:14,910
Come over!

31
00:03:16,790 --> 00:03:18,250
It seems the angrier he is,

32
00:03:18,380 --> 00:03:19,100
the more the Spirit Swords

33
