39
00:03:30,070 --> 00:03:31,079
Do you dare to admit

40
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:31,900
why you tricked me

41
00:03:31,900 --> 00:03:32,900
to this mountain?

42
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:34,110
You just want

43
00:03:34,140 --> 00:03:35,230
my Formless Spirit Root

44
00:03:35,230 --> 00:03:36,490
for your cultivation!

45
00:03:36,790 --> 00:03:38,860
How do you know about the Formless Spirit Root?

46
00:03:38,860 --> 00:03:40,900
What is done by night, appears by day.

47
00:03:40,900 --> 00:03:42,230
I won't let you succeed.

48
00:03:42,380 --> 00:03:43,540
I'll run so far away

49
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:44,720
so you never find me!

50
00:03:45,340 --> 00:03:46,270
