51
00:03:46,790 --> 00:03:48,550
You'll die if you leave Mount Wester.

52
00:03:48,550 --> 00:03:49,940
I'll die if I stay!

53
00:03:50,829 --> 00:03:52,470
You dared to kill your own master.

54
00:03:52,470 --> 00:03:53,100
What else

55
00:03:53,100 --> 00:03:53,829
can't you do?

56
