60
00:03:59,940 --> 00:04:00,790
Dream on!

61
00:04:02,540 --> 00:04:03,200
Xue Ranran.

62
00:04:04,420 --> 00:04:05,080
Xue Ranran!

63
00:04:11,100 --> 00:04:12,230
