We've come some way

94
00:05:21,290 --> 00:05:22,590
from Mount Wester, yeah?

95
00:05:22,590 --> 00:05:23,800
About 30 miles away.

96
00:05:26,030 --> 00:05:26,660
Thank you.

97
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:46,090
