00:14:29,070 --> 00:14:30,000
Mr. Zeng is here.

206
00:14:48,100 --> 00:14:50,260
It's been days since I've seen your face,

207
00:14:50,260 --> 00:14:51,790
but it's still as annoying.

208
00:14:54,870 --> 00:14:56,650
You've been practicing the Ice Lotus Technique so much

209
00:14:56,650 --> 00:14:58,090
that you're turning into a lump of ice.

210
00:14:56,740 --> 00:14:58,990
[Zeng Yi, disciple of Mu Qingge]

211
00:14:58,470 --> 00:14:59,700
Zero warmth.

212
00:15:00,660 --> 00:15:02,260
I called you here for something serious,

213
00:15:02,260 --> 00:15:03,990
not to listen to your nonsense.

214
00:15:05,140 --> 00:15:05,950
How is Master?

215
00:15:15,030 --> 00:15:15,660
Master.

216
00:15:17,030 --> 00:15:19,290
So this is how she looks like in this life.

217
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:20,470
You really

218
00:15:20,470 --> 00:15:22,270
disguised her appearance well.

219
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:29,390
You sent a letter that

220
00:15:29,510 --> 00:15:30,740
Master isn't feeling well

221
00:15:30,740 --> 00:15:31,990
and might be in danger.

222
00:15:31,990 --> 00:15:33,060
What's going on?

223
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,550
Her Reincarnation Fruit

224
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:36,470
fell too early,

225
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:38,400
so she was born

226
00:15:38,430 --> 00:15:39,560
with a broken heart.

227
00:15:39,900 --> 00:15:41,100
She can only survive by relying

228
00:15:41,100 --> 00:15:42,050
on the Reincarnation Tree's

229
00:15:42,050 --> 00:15:43,050
spiritual power.

230
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:45,390
If she's too far from the Tree,

231
00:15:45,390 --> 00:15:46,850
her life will be in danger.

232
00:15:47,620 --> 00:15:48,880
How could this happen?

233
00:15:50,260 --> 00:15:51,950
She even showed signs of premature aging

234
00:15:51,950 --> 00:15:52,660
after running

235
00:15:52,660 --> 00:15:53,990
away from the mountain.

236
00:15:55,300 --> 00:15:56,590
Something's off.

237
00:15:56,780 --> 00:15:57,430
So I need you to

238
00:15:57,430 --> 00:15:59,090
examine her with your energy.

239
00:16:08,700 --> 00:16:10,630
This Mirror will take half an hour.

240
00:16:16,100 --> 00:16:16,910
Once I got here,

241
00:16:16,910 --> 00:16:18,770
I asked Yu Tong about everything.

242
00:16:19,070 --> 00:16:21,140
Since you brought her to Mount Wester,

243
00:16:21,140 --> 00:16:22,870
you've always been cold to her.

244
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:23,870
You even kept making her

245
00:16:23,870 --> 00:16:24,660
go to intense places

246
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:26,620
like the Ice Lotus Pool or Westerly Valley.

247
00:16:26,620 --> 00:16:27,640
I know you want to

248
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:29,390
cleanse her meridians quickly.

249
00:16:29,390 --> 00:16:31,390
But without spiritual foundation,

250
00:16:31,510 --> 00:16:32,700
how can she bear it?

251
00:16:33,350 --> 00:16:34,220
Now, I'm her master

252
00:16:34,220 --> 00:16:35,480
and she's my disciple.

253
00:16:35,510 --> 00:16:36,510
How I discipline her

254
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:37,110
is up to me.

255
00:16:37,780 --> 00:16:38,310
Besides,

256
00:16:38,470 --> 00:16:39,780
my army's efforts were in vain

257
00:16:39,780 --> 00:16:41,700
because she eradicated my techniques.

258
00:16:41,700 --> 00:16:42,550
I'm already being

259
00:16:42,550 --> 00:16:43,620
as gracious as I can.

260
00:16:43,620 --> 00:16:44,660
I'm at my limit.

261
00:16:46,260 --> 00:16:47,430
After so many years,

262
00:16:48,070 --> 00:16:50,000
you've only become more stubborn.

263
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:51,450
Back then, Master knew

264
00:16:51,450 --> 00:16:53,380
you were about to attain ascension

265
00:16:53,470 --> 00:16:54,530
and so the Burning Curse

266
00:16:54,530 --> 00:16:55,390
will be lifted.

267
00:16:55,740 --> 00:16:57,000
If you really hate her,

268
00:16:57,300 --> 00:16:58,830
why'd you give up your ascension

269
00:16:58,830 --> 00:17:01,030
and half of your Golden Core to save her?

270
00:17:01,430 --> 00:17:02,740
You even claimed it was

271
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:03,820
about saving

272
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:04,550
Wester Sect.

273
00:17:04,569 --> 00:17:05,530
How ridiculous.

274
00:17:06,260 --> 00:17:07,660
She did die because of me.

275
00:17:07,930 --> 00:17:08,890
I owe her my life.

276
00:17:10,030 --> 00:17:11,300
Once her heart is stable

277
00:17:11,300 --> 00:17:12,050
and she's self-sufficient,

278
00:17:12,050 --> 00:17:13,780
I'll make her leave right away.

279
00:17:14,619 --> 00:17:15,349
Don't lie.

280
00:17:16,990 --> 00:17:19,390
You were a difficult person a dozen years ago.

281
00:17:19,390 --> 00:17:20,030
Now,

282
00:17:20,030 --> 00:17:21,560
you're still as difficult.

283
00:17:22,420 --> 00:17:24,450
Master put the Face-and-Heart Burning Curse on you

