00:17:26,490 --> 00:17:28,750
She hoped everything would end with her.

286
00:17:29,010 --> 00:17:30,770
If you hadn't sincerely repented

287
00:17:30,770 --> 00:17:33,050
and lived a life worse than death for 18 years,

288
00:17:33,050 --> 00:17:34,630
I certainly wouldn't have forgiven you.

289
00:17:34,630 --> 00:17:36,210
Don't expect any of the other disciples

290
00:17:36,210 --> 00:17:37,370
to treat you kindly.

291
00:17:37,900 --> 00:17:38,900
I don't need that.

292
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,730
Master treated you so differently,

293
00:17:41,730 --> 00:17:42,930
and even died for you,

294
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:44,860
yet you're still so stubborn.

295
00:17:44,860 --> 00:17:46,190
What's the difference?

296
00:17:46,490 --> 00:17:47,380
If this had happened

297
00:17:47,380 --> 00:17:48,380
to you back then,

298
00:17:48,490 --> 00:17:49,210
or to any other

299
00:17:49,210 --> 00:17:49,860
disciple,

300
00:17:49,860 --> 00:17:51,460
she would have done the same.

301
00:17:53,730 --> 00:17:55,130
It just happened to be me.

302
00:17:56,530 --> 00:17:58,050
She did it for her own path,

303
00:17:58,420 --> 00:17:59,900
for the greater good of the universe,

304
00:17:59,900 --> 00:18:00,690
for the peaceful and prosperous world

305
00:18:00,690 --> 00:18:02,150
she cherished in her eyes,

306
00:18:02,470 --> 00:18:03,770
and for the benevolent ruler

307
00:18:03,770 --> 00:18:06,300
she believed was more suitable for this land.

308
00:18:06,450 --> 00:18:08,250
But she still died because of me.

309
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:10,010
I will never be indebted to her.

310
00:18:10,010 --> 00:18:10,450
You...

311
00:18:13,040 --> 00:18:16,150
[Carefree Pavilion]

312
00:18:23,780 --> 00:18:24,940
What's going on?

313
00:18:42,530 --> 00:18:44,260
It's the Soul-Devouring Lock.

314
00:18:45,530 --> 00:18:46,450
It's the evil magic weapon

315
00:18:46,450 --> 00:18:48,140
that is said to be able to absorb completely

316
00:18:48,140 --> 00:18:49,320
others' spiritual power

317
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:50,380
until they perish.

318
00:18:51,010 --> 00:18:51,660
How did she

319
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:52,730
get it inside her?

320
00:18:52,970 --> 00:18:53,700
Who did this?

321
00:18:54,380 --> 00:18:55,510
Who else could it be?

322
00:18:55,940 --> 00:18:56,530
Mu Ranwu.

323
00:18:57,530 --> 00:18:58,100
I thought

324
00:18:58,100 --> 00:18:58,970
she was forced by the Heavenly

325
00:18:58,970 --> 00:18:59,970
to do this.

326
00:19:01,210 --> 00:19:03,140
I didn't expect it was all planned.

327
00:19:03,580 --> 00:19:04,450
It seems she wanted to steal

328
00:19:04,450 --> 00:19:05,580
Mu Qingge's spiritual power.

329
00:19:05,580 --> 00:19:08,640
That's why she entered the formation and lost her life.

330
00:19:19,710 --> 00:19:21,320
Master was her only family.

331
00:19:22,180 --> 00:19:22,900
Moreover, at that time,

332
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:23,620
Master was so good to her.

333
00:19:23,620 --> 00:19:24,950
How could she do this?

334
00:19:25,340 --> 00:19:26,570
We'll settle her score later.

335
00:19:26,570 --> 00:19:28,340
Let's remove the Soul-Devouring Lock first.

336
00:19:28,340 --> 00:19:28,870
Alright.

337
00:19:29,180 --> 00:19:29,710
I'll try.

338
00:19:38,620 --> 00:19:39,550
What's going on?

339
00:19:50,210 --> 00:19:51,340
I didn't expect that

340
00:19:51,730 --> 00:19:54,120
this Soul-Devouring Lock would merge with her heart

341
00:19:54,120 --> 00:19:55,580
after her reincarnation.

342
00:19:56,340 --> 00:19:58,140
Master's heart is unstable now.

343
00:19:58,250 --> 00:19:59,730
If we rashly remove the lock,

344
00:19:59,730 --> 00:20:02,190
I'm afraid she won't be able to withstand it.

345
00:20:02,250 --> 00:20:03,080
Mu Ranwu will be born

346
00:20:03,080 --> 00:20:04,190
in three months.

347
00:20:05,140 --> 00:20:06,940
Once she advances in the future,

348
00:20:06,970 --> 00:20:08,490
as one rises, the other falls,

349
00:20:08,490 --> 00:20:09,820
Master will surely die.

350
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:11,910
Then I'll just kill her.

351
00:20:12,010 --> 00:20:12,810
No, you can't.

352
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:14,290
The Soul-Devouring Lock has bound the two of them

353
00:20:14,290 --> 00:20:15,350
tightly together.

354
00:20:15,620 --> 00:20:16,340
If she dies,

355
00:20:16,770 --> 00:20:17,900
Master will die too.

356
00:20:20,270 --> 00:20:21,340
Now we can only help Master

357
00:20:21,340 --> 00:20:22,860
increase her spiritual power as quickly as possible.

358
00:20:22,860 --> 00:20:24,390
Stabilize her heart first.

359
00:20:24,490 --> 00:20:27,020
We'll figure out how to remove the lock later.

360
00:20:33,140 --> 00:20:35,450
Fortunately, Master is blessed by heaven.

361
00:20:35,450 --> 00:20:36,940
Although her Five Spirit Roots were taken,

362
00:20:36,940 --> 00:20:38,560
it was a blessing in disguise.

363
00:20:38,560 --> 00:20:40,050
It has been reborn as a Formless Spirit Root

364
00:20:40,050 --> 00:20:41,910
through the Reincarnation Tree.

365
00:20:43,380 --> 00:20:44,450
What are you going to do?

366
00:20:44,450 --> 00:20:46,050
If it weren't for you,

367
00:20:46,210 --> 00:20:47,050
how could Mu Ranwu possibly

368
00:20:47,050 --> 00:20:48,050
have had the opportunity?

369
00:20:48,050 --> 00:20:49,320
Master can't stay here.

370
00:20:49,320 --> 00:20:50,570
I'm taking her back to my Tea Inscription Mountain.

371
00:20:50,570 --> 00:20:51,430
Don't you dare!

372
00:20:51,580 --> 00:20:52,770
I'm taking my Master away.

373
00:20:52,770 --> 00:20:54,570
What right do you have to stop me?

374
00:20:54,640 --> 00:20:55,420
If you keep Master here,

375
00:20:55,420 --> 00:20:56,550
what good will it do?

376
00:20:57,360 --> 00:20:57,770
When Master remembers all

377
00:20:57,770 --> 00:20:59,010
in the future,

378
00:20:59,580 --> 00:21:00,770
do you think she will forgive you

379
00:21:00,770 --> 00:21:01,900
for the harm and betrayal

380
00:21:01,900 --> 00:21:03,140
you have done to her?

381
00:21:03,770 --> 00:21:04,420
No matter what she does to you

382
00:21:04,420 --> 00:21:05,450
in the future,

383
00:21:05,860 --> 00:21:06,860
you'll have to

384
00:21:06,940 --> 00:21:08,210
bear the blood debt you owe alone.

385
00:21:08,210 --> 00:21:10,140
If she doesn't forgive me, so be it.

386
00:21:10,290 --> 00:21:11,890
I'll pay for her with my life.

387
00:21:13,940 --> 00:21:15,450
If she wants to kill me,

388
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:17,530
I'll prepare the knife for her.

389
00:21:17,530 --> 00:21:19,140
If she never wants to see me again,

390
00:21:19,140 --> 00:21:20,370
I'll arrange everything for her

391
00:21:20,370 --> 00:21:21,370
and send her away.

392
00:21:21,940 --> 00:21:22,820
I swore that

393
00:21:23,620 --> 00:21:25,420
I would protect her in this life,

394
00:21:25,530 --> 00:21:27,010
and no one, including me,

395
00:21:27,860 --> 00:21:28,730
could hurt her.

396
00:21:30,690 --> 00:21:31,290
Moreover,

397
00:21:32,110 --> 00:21:33,010
I still have some questions

398
00:21:33,010 --> 00:21:34,410
that remain unanswered.

399
00:21:35,050 --> 00:21:37,180
Back then, before the Heavenly siege,

400
00:21:37,290 --> 00:21:38,530
she was already severely injured.

401
00:21:38,530 --> 00:21:39,420
Who hurt her?

402
00:21:41,340 --> 00:21:42,270
And at that time,

403
00:21:42,580 --> 00:21:44,190
if she wanted to carry the Spirit Spring with her,

404
00:21:44,190 --> 00:21:45,010
suppressing the Spirit Spring

405
00:21:45,010 --> 00:21:46,140
wasn't impossible.

406
00:21:46,260 --> 00:21:47,620
Why did she rush to seal it with the Golden Core

407
00:21:47,620 --> 00:21:49,180
and hide it in Wangxiang Pass?

408
00:21:49,180 --> 00:21:50,690
What exactly did she encounter?

409
00:21:50,690 --> 00:21:52,210
There must be something behind this.

410
00:21:52,210 --> 00:21:53,340
I must figure it out.

411
00:21:53,420 --> 00:21:55,680
I must remove this Soul-Devouring Lock.

412
00:22:20,010 --> 00:22:21,180
Work hard.

413
00:22:21,380 --> 00:22:23,440
Complete the task I entrusted to you.

414
00:22:23,690 --> 00:22:24,660
Then, you and I,

415
00:22:25,250 --> 00:22:26,450
for all lifetimes,

416
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:28,180
shall never meet again.

417
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:30,310
Every injustice has its perpetrator.

418
00:22:31,350 --> 00:22:33,100
Go look for the one who made you die

419
00:22:33,100 --> 00:22:34,250
beyond recognition.

420
00:22:34,250 --> 00:22:35,340
It's not my fault.

421
00:22:36,290 --> 00:22:37,950
You don't remember anything?

422
00:22:47,210 --> 00:22:48,620
To incorporate the Ice Lotus into your technique,

423
00:22:48,620 --> 00:22:50,580
you must cultivate it without emotions.

424
00:22:50,580 --> 00:22:52,310
Otherwise, when your seven emotions are disturbed,

425
00:22:52,310 --> 00:22:53,970
the technique will backfire.

426
00:22:54,050 --> 00:22:55,590
The Ice Lotus in your body

427
00:22:55,620 --> 00:22:58,010
will turn into ice needles piercing into the bloodstream,

428
00:22:58,010 --> 00:22:59,420
making you feel so painful

429
00:22:59,420 --> 00:23:00,880
that you would rather die.

430
00:23:00,940 --> 00:23:02,070
Don't be obsessive!

431
00:23:04,940 --> 00:23:05,740
Disillusion!

432
00:23:14,820 --> 00:23:15,620
What's wrong?

433
00:23:15,660 --> 00:23:17,290
I can't even criticize you?

434
00:23:18,050 --> 00:23:19,530
What's with your attitude?

435
00:23:19,530 --> 00:23:21,180
You were the one who treated Master badly.

436
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:23,180
Otherwise, would she have run away?

437
00:23:23,210 --> 00:23:25,250
You're confused and can't figure out your own feelings.

438
00:23:25,250 --> 00:23:26,710
Why are you torturing her?

439
00:23:27,420 --> 00:23:28,490
Immortal Master, you've misunderstood.

440
00:23:28,490 --> 00:23:30,550
Guardian has never done such things.

441
00:23:32,530 --> 00:23:33,290
Actually,

442
00:23:33,940 --> 00:23:36,200
Guardian is the one bearing everything.

443
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:43,530
It doesn't hurt much anymore.

444
00:23:51,450 --> 00:23:52,140
Really?

445
00:23:52,490 --> 00:23:53,010
Guardian has always

446
00:23:53,010 --> 00:23:54,140
transferred her cultivation hardships

447
00:23:54,140 --> 00:23:55,870
through immortal techniques.

448
00:23:56,100 --> 00:23:57,700
He just never said anything.

449
00:24:02,690 --> 00:24:04,580
There's no need to say anything to him.

450
00:24:04,580 --> 00:24:05,100
I...

451
00:24:06,820 --> 00:24:07,340
Look.

452
00:24:07,820 --> 00:24:09,250
He's just

453
00:24:09,250 --> 00:24:10,140
too arrogant.

454
00:24:10,970 --> 00:24:12,100
I really don't know how you and Yu Chen

455
00:24:12,100 --> 00:24:12,690
have endured it

456
00:24:12,690 --> 00:24:13,620
all these years.

457
00:24:22,580 --> 00:24:23,380
You're awake.

458
00:24:26,290 --> 00:24:28,220
Go ahead and ask whatever you want.

459
00:24:29,050 --> 00:24:30,340
Why did I become like that

460
00:24:30,340 --> 00:24:31,800
after I left the mountain?

461
00:24:39,420 --> 00:24:41,490
What does it have to do with this branch?

462
00:24:41,490 --> 00:24:43,020
You were born prematurely,

463
00:24:43,100 --> 00:24:44,030
weak from birth.

464
00:24:44,450 --> 00:24:45,050
Even your heart,

465
00:24:45,050 --> 00:24:46,910
the source of life, was unstable.

466
00:24:46,960 --> 00:24:48,890
That's why your life was in danger.

467
00:24:49,940 --> 00:24:50,690
So

468
00:24:50,970 --> 00:24:52,340
your master brought back

469
00:24:52,340 --> 00:24:54,010
this branch from the Reincarnation Tree

470
00:24:54,010 --> 00:24:55,540
to connect with your heart,

471
00:24:55,820 --> 00:24:57,690
providing you with life-sustaining spiritual power.

472
00:24:57,690 --> 00:24:58,970
If you're too far from the branch,

473
00:24:58,970 --> 00:25:00,100
the spiritual power will be insufficient,

474
00:25:00,100 --> 00:25:01,830
and your life will be in danger.

475
00:25:02,250 --> 00:25:03,820
Keeping you on the mountain to practice

476
00:25:03,820 --> 00:25:05,950
was also to help stabilize your heart.

477
00:25:09,520 --> 00:25:10,860
Ranran, don't be afraid.

478
00:25:10,860 --> 00:25:12,290
I am

479
00:25:14,490 --> 00:25:15,580
Mr. Zeng.

480
00:25:18,380 --> 00:25:19,220
My name is

481
00:25:19,250 --> 00:25:19,860
Zeng Yi.

482
00:25:20,500 --> 00:25:21,350
With me here,

483
00:25:21,380 --> 00:25:22,380
on this mountain,

484
00:25:22,420 --> 00:25:23,690
no one can bully you.

485
00:25:26,420 --> 00:25:27,760
Mr. Zeng.

486
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:40,430
What are you looking at?

487
00:25:40,970 --> 00:25:42,650
There's no thunder here.

488
00:25:43,140 --> 00:25:43,830
I mean

489
00:25:44,250 --> 00:25:45,490
the weather today

490
00:25:45,770 --> 00:25:46,380
is nice.

491
00:25:58,290 --> 00:25:59,290
I see.

492
00:26:00,490 --> 00:26:02,380
Then why didn't you tell me earlier?

493
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:03,580
How could I have known

494
00:26:03,620 --> 00:26:04,900
you would be so ridiculous

495
00:26:04,900 --> 00:26:06,430
to think I wanted to eat you?

496
00:26:07,020 --> 00:26:08,300
That's your problem.

497
00:26:08,970 --> 00:26:10,830
You're always looking so fierce,

498
00:26:11,010 --> 00:26:12,870
no wonder you scared Ranran away.

499
00:26:13,290 --> 00:26:14,770
The misunderstanding earlier

500
00:26:14,770 --> 00:26:15,660
was my fault.

501
00:26:16,420 --> 00:26:18,080
But I still don't understand.

502
00:26:18,580 --> 00:26:20,180
You and I met by chance.

503
00:26:20,690 --> 00:26:22,820
Why are you taking such good care of me?

504
00:26:26,450 --> 00:26:28,420
He owes it to someone else.

505
00:26:28,730 --> 00:26:30,100
He should do this.

506
00:26:30,690 --> 00:26:32,020
Owes it to someone else?

507
00:26:33,420 --> 00:26:34,830
Could it be my parents?

508
00:26:35,450 --> 00:26:36,050
No.

509
00:26:39,530 --> 00:26:40,380
Then who is it?

510
00:26:41,420 --> 00:26:43,490
Could it be Master's friend?

511
00:26:43,660 --> 00:26:44,770
-Yes.
-No.

512
00:26:55,380 --> 00:26:56,180
I understand.

513
00:26:56,860 --> 00:26:57,920
If that's the case,

514
00:26:58,050 --> 00:26:59,530
then thank you, Master,

515
00:26:59,530 --> 00:27:00,730
for taking care of me.

516
00:27:01,380 --> 00:27:02,310
You want to stay?

517
00:27:05,140 --> 00:27:06,940
Since I can only survive

518
00:27:06,970 --> 00:27:08,140
by staying and practicing on Mount Wester,

519
00:27:08,140 --> 00:27:09,270
then I'll practice.

520
00:27:09,730 --> 00:27:11,900
Although Master didn't make it clear today,

521
00:27:11,900 --> 00:27:13,360
he has saved me many times.

522
00:27:13,490 --> 00:27:14,950
I believe he won't harm me.

523
00:27:15,860 --> 00:27:17,280
When he's ready to tell me,

524
00:27:17,280 --> 00:27:18,410
it won't be too late.

525
00:27:30,580 --> 00:27:32,100
Carry it with you from now on

526
00:27:32,100 --> 00:27:33,830
to prevent any more accidents.

527
00:27:33,940 --> 00:27:35,490
Although the Reincarnation Tree is good,

528
00:27:35,490 --> 00:27:37,860
its spiritual power will eventually be depleted.

529
00:27:37,860 --> 00:27:39,180
If you want to stay alive,

530
00:27:39,180 --> 00:27:41,210
you still need to practice diligently.

531
00:27:41,210 --> 00:27:42,010
I understand.

532
00:27:43,210 --> 00:27:43,810
Oh, right.

533
00:27:44,730 --> 00:27:46,330
I have something to confess.

534
00:27:46,970 --> 00:27:48,450
When I came up the mountain before,

535
00:27:48,450 --> 00:27:50,010
I had my own plan.

536
00:27:50,970 --> 00:27:52,430
I wanted to save my friend.

537
00:27:52,770 --> 00:27:53,620
Your friend?

538
00:27:58,450 --> 00:28:00,140
It's a fragment of a spiritual soul.

539
00:28:00,140 --> 00:28:02,350
It's been away from its owner for too long and is close to death.

540
00:28:02,350 --> 00:28:03,620
It's said that only Liang Wumeng

541
00:28:03,620 --> 00:28:05,450
can save it by using the Blood Chalcedony.

542
00:28:05,450 --> 00:28:06,210
That's why

543
00:28:06,970 --> 00:28:08,860
I took your Blood Chalcedony.

544
00:28:10,690 --> 00:28:11,570
Just for this thing,

545
00:28:11,570 --> 00:28:12,970
you're willing to risk your life?

546
00:28:12,970 --> 00:28:14,770
Do you value your life so little?

547
00:28:16,580 --> 00:28:17,640
What are you doing?

548
00:28:17,860 --> 00:28:18,990
Mind your attitude.

549
00:28:19,210 --> 00:28:20,740
Ranran has just recovered.

550
00:28:20,970 --> 00:28:22,250
Since I can remember,

551
00:28:22,530 --> 00:28:24,460
Ling Xiao has always protected me.

552
00:28:24,860 --> 00:28:26,590
It's my most important friend.

553
00:28:26,860 --> 00:28:28,660
I can't stand by and watch it die.

554
00:28:30,180 --> 00:28:31,510
So you left the mountain

555
00:28:31,970 --> 00:28:33,570
to save this spiritual soul.

556
00:28:35,140 --> 00:28:36,770
What a bad fate!

557
00:28:37,990 --> 00:28:39,290
Once I find Liang Wumeng

558
00:28:39,290 --> 00:28:40,420
and save Ling Xiao,

559
00:28:40,690 --> 00:28:41,450
I promise to focus on

560
00:28:41,450 --> 00:28:43,110
cultivation on the mountain.

561
00:28:43,350 --> 00:28:45,140
As for your Blood Chalcedony,

562
00:28:45,940 --> 00:28:47,010
I'll find a new one

563
00:28:47,010 --> 00:28:48,210
to replace it for you.

564
00:28:48,210 --> 00:28:48,940
Is that okay?

565
00:28:56,770 --> 00:28:58,610
[Liang Wumeng's residence]

566
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:07,390
This is

567
00:29:07,420 --> 00:29:08,950
Liang Wumeng's residence?

568
00:29:08,970 --> 00:29:09,770
That's right.

569
00:29:14,010 --> 00:29:14,690
Sorry.

570
00:29:15,140 --> 00:29:17,140
Master is currently in seclusion

571
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:18,680
and cannot receive visitors.

